sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Gateway
    participant Auth
    participant UserSvc
    participant OrderSvc
    participant PaymentSvc
    participant NotifySvc
    participant DB

    Client->>Gateway: POST /orders
    Gateway->>Auth: Validate token
    Auth-->>Gateway: Token valid
    Gateway->>OrderSvc: Create order
    OrderSvc->>DB: Check inventory
    DB-->>OrderSvc: Items available
    OrderSvc->>PaymentSvc: Process payment
    PaymentSvc->>PaymentSvc: Validate card
    PaymentSvc-->>OrderSvc: Payment confirmed
    OrderSvc->>DB: Save order
    DB-->>OrderSvc: Order saved
    OrderSvc->>NotifySvc: Send confirmation
    NotifySvc->>Client: Email sent
    OrderSvc-->>Gateway: Order created
    Gateway-->>Client: 201 Created
